Install packages using pip according to requirements.txt file. Run the command below in terminal:
$ pip install -r requirements.txt

To run the test use the following command:
py.test -s -v tests/home/login_tests.py

To generate html report install a plugin with the command: 
pip install pytest-html

To generate a HTML report for a Selenium test,use command:
py.test -s -v --html=report.html tests/home/login_tests.py

